# APPEND-ONLY REGISTRY RULE v1.0
## Quy tắc bất biến cho registry management

```yaml
# HEADER
header:
  id: RC://rule.append-only-registry.v1
  intent: DECLARE_RULE
  status: LOCKED
  locale: vi-85
  
metadata:
  fractal_name: "ros.rule.registry.append-only"
  lazy_type: "immutability_rule"
  version: "1.0"
  seal_date: "2025-02-23"
  hash_anchor: "{{to_be_sealed}}"
  
dependencies:
  constitution:
    - "poly-ledger-anchor-law.clo"
    - "seal-integrity-law.clo"
  protocol:
    - "registry-freeze-protocol.clo"
```

---

## 🎯 MỤC ĐÍCH

Quy tắc này đảm bảo registry (.olym) **không bao giờ bị overwrite, rename, hay delete**, 
chỉ được **append** và **supersede** theo version control.

**Mục tiêu 10 năm:** Cấu trúc folder không thay đổi, deterministic loading, zero jitter.

---

## 📜 NGUYÊN TẮC CỐT LÕI

### 1️⃣ Append-Only Principle

```yaml
principle:
  name: "APPEND_ONLY"
  rule: "Chỉ thêm, không sửa, không xóa"
  
  allowed_operations:
    - action: "append_version"
      condition: "Tạo vX.X+1.clo mới"
      example: "override-precedence-law/v1.1.clo"
      
    - action: "append_seal_log"
      condition: "Ghi thêm hash vào seal.log"
      example: "seal.log += 'v1.1 → SHA256:abc...'"
      
    - action: "append_changelog"
      condition: "Ghi lý do version bump"
      example: "changelog.ail += 'v1.1: Fixed authority boundary'"
  
  forbidden_operations:
    - action: "overwrite_file"
      penalty: "REJECT_COMMIT"
      
    - action: "rename_folder"
      penalty: "REJECT_COMMIT"
      
    - action: "delete_version"
      penalty: "REJECT_COMMIT"
      
    - action: "force_downgrade"
      penalty: "SYSTEM_HALT"
```

---

## 🗂️ CẤU TRÚC FRACTAL FOLDER

### Domain Root (Immutable Spine)

```yaml
immutable_spine:
  path: "t:/hace/.olym/"
  
  domains:
    - name: "constitution"
      status: "IMMUTABLE"
      rule: "Không được thêm/xóa/đổi tên domain này"
      
    - name: "engine"
      status: "IMMUTABLE"
      rule: "Không được thêm/xóa/đổi tên domain này"
      
    - name: "protocol"
      status: "IMMUTABLE"
      rule: "Không được thêm/xóa/đổi tên domain này"
      
    - name: "rule"
      status: "IMMUTABLE"
      rule: "Không được thêm/xóa/đổi tên domain này"
      
    - name: "spec"
      status: "IMMUTABLE"
      rule: "Không được thêm/xóa/đổi tên domain này"
      
    - name: "blueprint"
      status: "IMMUTABLE"
      rule: "Không được thêm/xóa/đổi tên domain này"
      
    - name: "term"
      status: "IMMUTABLE"
      rule: "Không được thêm/xóa/đổi tên domain này"
  
  expansion_rule:
    allowed: true
    condition: "Chỉ được thêm domain mới qua constitutional amendment"
    example: "Nếu cần domain 'adapter', phải qua Core Four governance"
```

---

## 📁 Object Folder Pattern

### Standard Structure

```yaml
object_pattern:
  structure: |
    <domain>/<object-name>/
    ├── v1.0.clo        # First sealed version
    ├── v1.1.clo        # Refinement
    ├── v2.0.clo        # Major revision
    ├── changelog.ail   # Version history
    ├── seal.log        # Hash anchors
    └── links.ail       # Cross-references
  
  rules:
    - "Object phải là folder, không phải file trực tiếp"
    - "Version file theo pattern vX.Y.clo"
    - "Mỗi version phải có entry trong seal.log"
    - "changelog.ail là append-only log"
```

---

## 🔢 VERSION DISCIPLINE

### Version Bumping Rules

```yaml
versioning:
  major_bump:
    trigger: "Breaking change trong API/interface"
    pattern: "v1.0 → v2.0"
    example: "override-precedence-law thay đổi weight formula"
    
  minor_bump:
    trigger: "Refinement, clarification, non-breaking fix"
    pattern: "v1.0 → v1.1"
    example: "Bổ sung ví dụ, sửa typo logic"
    
  forbidden:
    - action: "Sửa file cũ"
      why: "Phá vỡ hash anchor"
      
    - action: "Xóa version cũ"
      why: "Mất lịch sử audit"
      
    - action: "Rename version file"
      why: "Gây confusion cho loader"
```

---

## 🔐 SEAL LOG DISCIPLINE

### Seal.log Format

```yaml
seal_format:
  file: "seal.log"
  structure: |
    # SEAL LOG - APPEND ONLY
    v1.0 | 2025-02-23T08:00:00Z | SHA256:abc123... | LOCKED
    v1.1 | 2025-02-24T10:30:00Z | SHA256:def456... | ACTIVE
  
  rules:
    - "Mỗi version phải có 1 entry"
    - "Entry không được sửa/xóa"
    - "Hash phải match với file content"
    - "Status: DRAFT → LOCKED → DEPRECATED"
```

---

## 📋 CHANGELOG DISCIPLINE

### Changelog.ail Format

```yaml
changelog_format:
  file: "changelog.ail"
  structure: |
    # CHANGELOG - APPEND ONLY
    
    ## v1.1 (2025-02-24)
    ### Changed
    - Refined authority weight calculation
    - Added cross-domain conflict example
    
    ### Why
    - User feedback: unclear precedence in edge case
    
    ## v1.0 (2025-02-23)
    ### Initial Release
    - Established append-only principle
  
  rules:
    - "Mỗi version phải có section riêng"
    - "Phải ghi rõ lý do thay đổi (Why)"
    - "Không được sửa entry cũ"
```

---

## 🔗 CROSS-REFERENCE MODEL

### Links.ail Pattern

```yaml
links_model:
  file: "links.ail"
  purpose: "Track dependencies without embedding content"
  
  structure: |
    # LINKS - Cross-domain references
    
    references:
      constitution:
        - id: "authority-boundary-law"
          version: "v1.0"
          reason: "Authority weight definition"
      
      engine:
        - id: "engine-authority-map"
          version: "v1.0"
          reason: "Implementation reference"
  
  rules:
    - "Không embed content từ file khác"
    - "Chỉ link tới version cụ thể"
    - "Phải ghi rõ lý do reference"
```

---

## 📊 MASTER INDEX CONTROL

### Master/index.clo Authority

```yaml
master_index:
  location: "t:/hace/.olym/master/index.clo"
  authority: "ROOT"
  
  responsibilities:
    - "Pointer tới active version của mỗi object"
    - "Status tracking (DRAFT/LOCKED/DEPRECATED)"
    - "Cross-domain integrity check"
  
  example:
    objects:
      - id: "override-precedence-law"
        domain: "constitution"
        active_version: "v1.1"
        status: "LOCKED"
        last_update: "2025-02-24"
      
      - id: "append-only-registry-rule"
        domain: "rule"
        active_version: "v1.0"
        status: "LOCKED"
        last_update: "2025-02-23"
  
  update_rules:
    - "Chỉ được update active_version pointer"
    - "Không được xóa object entry"
    - "Status chỉ được: DRAFT → LOCKED → DEPRECATED"
    - "Deprecated object vẫn giữ entry"
```

---

## 🚫 FORBIDDEN OPERATIONS

```yaml
forbidden:
  overwrite:
    example: "echo 'new' > v1.0.clo"
    penalty: "REJECT_COMMIT"
    reason: "Phá vỡ seal integrity"
  
  rename:
    example: "mv override-precedence-law precedence-law"
    penalty: "REJECT_COMMIT"
    reason: "Gây confusion cho loader deterministic path"
  
  delete:
    example: "rm v1.0.clo"
    penalty: "REJECT_COMMIT"
    reason: "Mất audit trail"
  
  force_downgrade:
    example: "active_version: v1.1 → v1.0"
    penalty: "SYSTEM_HALT"
    reason: "Vi phạm seal-integrity-law"
  
  domain_mutation:
    example: "mv constitution/obj rule/obj"
    penalty: "CONSTITUTION_VIOLATION"
    reason: "Domain boundary không được vi phạm"
```

---

## ✅ ALLOWED OPERATIONS

```yaml
allowed:
  version_append:
    action: "Tạo v1.1.clo mới"
    condition: "v1.0.clo phải đã LOCKED"
    flow:
      1: "Copy v1.0.clo → draft/v1.1.clo"
      2: "Edit draft/v1.1.clo"
      3: "Seal → v1.1.clo"
      4: "Append seal.log"
      5: "Update master/index.clo pointer"
  
  seal_append:
    action: "Ghi hash mới vào seal.log"
    condition: "Version mới đã pass integrity check"
    format: "v1.1 | timestamp | hash | LOCKED"
  
  changelog_append:
    action: "Ghi version history"
    condition: "Mỗi version bump phải ghi changelog"
    format: "## vX.X (date)\n### Changed\n- ...\n### Why\n- ..."
  
  deprecation:
    action: "Mark object status = DEPRECATED"
    condition: "Có superseding object"
    rule: "Deprecated object vẫn giữ nguyên trong registry"
```

---

## 🧬 FRACTAL EXPANSION RULE

```yaml
expansion:
  new_object:
    allowed: true
    process:
      1: "Tạo <domain>/<new-object>/"
      2: "Tạo v1.0.clo, changelog.ail, seal.log"
      3: "Seal v1.0"
      4: "Update master/index.clo"
    
  new_domain:
    allowed: false
    exception: "Chỉ qua constitutional amendment"
    process:
      1: "Đề xuất tại Core Four governance"
      2: "Phê duyệt qua override-precedence-law"
      3: "Update master/master.ail semantic root"
      4: "Tạo domain folder"
      5: "Seal domain creation"
```

---

## 🔍 COMPLIANCE CHECK

### Pre-commit Hook

```yaml
compliance_check:
  trigger: "Before git commit"
  
  checks:
    - name: "no_overwrite"
      test: "git diff không có modification trong sealed files"
      
    - name: "no_rename"
      test: "git status không có renamed files"
      
    - name: "no_delete"
      test: "git status không có deleted files"
      
    - name: "seal_integrity"
      test: "Mỗi .clo mới phải có seal.log entry"
      
    - name: "changelog_present"
      test: "Version bump phải có changelog update"
  
  action_on_fail: "REJECT_COMMIT"
```

---

## 🎯 DETERMINISTIC LOADER BENEFIT

```yaml
loader_benefits:
  zero_jitter:
    reason: "Path không bao giờ thay đổi"
    example: "constitution/override-precedence-law/v1.0.clo"
    
  hash_verification:
    reason: "Seal.log cho phép verify integrity"
    example: "SHA256 match → trust"
    
  version_control:
    reason: "Active_version pointer trong index.clo"
    example: "Loader chỉ load version được point"
    
  audit_trail:
    reason: "Toàn bộ history được giữ lại"
    example: "Trace từ v1.0 → v1.1 → v2.0"
```

---

## 📐 CONFLICT RESOLUTION

```yaml
conflicts:
  same_domain_conflict:
    example: "2 objects cùng purpose trong rule/"
    resolution: "Dùng override-precedence-law để chọn"
    
  cross_domain_conflict:
    example: "rule vs constitution về cùng topic"
    resolution: "Constitution > rule (theo precedence weight)"
    
  version_conflict:
    example: "v1.0 vs v1.1 active"
    resolution: "Dùng master/index.clo pointer"
```

