## 📝 IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST

```yaml
implementation:
  step_1:
    task: "Tạo pre-commit hook"
    file: ".git/hooks/pre-commit"
    check: ["no_overwrite", "no_rename", "no_delete"]
    
  step_2:
    task: "Setup seal verification"
    tool: "SHA256 checksum"
    trigger: "Before load"
    
  step_3:
    task: "Enforce master/index.clo authority"
    rule: "Loader chỉ tin index.clo pointer"
    
  step_4:
    task: "Document changelog template"
    file: "master/templates/changelog.template.ail"
```

